<F P=103> HK3101023094 </F>
<F P=104>  Hong Kong WEN WEI PO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Dispatch by trainee reporter Li Hsiao-ping (2621 4562 </F>
0393): "In March, Li Peng Is To Attend a Meeting in Shenzhen on 
Renewing the Appointment of the Hong Kong Affairs Advisers and a 
Ceremony Marking the Supply of Dong Jiang Water to Hong Kong"] 
  [Text] Beijing, 30 Jan (WEN WEI PO) -- As disclosed by a 
