Committee of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region here, 
State Council Premier Li Peng will be attending a ceremony in 
Shenzhen on 1 March to mark the 29th anniversary of supplying 
water from the Dong Jiang to Hong Kong and a meeting on 2 March 
to renew the appointment of the first group of Hong Kong affairs 
advisers. 

