<H3> <TI>   Than Shwe Accepts Israeli Ambassador Credentials </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK2912144593 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 29 Dec 
93 </F>

<F P=103> BK2912144593 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon Radio Burma </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Burmese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Senior General Than Shwe, chairman of the State Law 
and Order Restoration Council [SLORC] of the Union of Burma, 
accepted the credentials of Mr. Mordechai Karni, ambassador 
extraordinary and plenipotentiary of Israel to the Union of 
