<H3> <TI>   Press Review for 31 Dec </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW3112144193 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1251 GMT 31 Dec 
93 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW3112144193 </F>
