Committee of the Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee 
and chairman of the Standing Committee of the National People's 
Congress of the PRC; Li Ruihuan, member of the Standing 
Committee of the Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee 
and chairman of the National Committee of the Chinese People's 
