Standing Committee of the Political Bureau of the CPC Central 
Committee; Chen Yun, former chairman of the Central Advisory 
Commission of the CPC; Yang Shangkun, former president of the 
PRC; Peng Zhen, former chairman of the Standing Committee of the 
National People's Congress of the PRC; Fidel Castro Ruz, first 
