president of the Republic of Ukraine; Zoran Lilic, president of 
the Federal Republic of Yugoslavia; Phoumi Vongvichit, advisor 
to the Central Committee of the Lao People's Revolutionary 
Party; H.S. Surjeet, general secretary of the Central Committee 
