in Korean 1300 GMT 30 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> SK3112005893 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network 
in Korean 1300 GMT 30 Dec 93 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Korean </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Kim Pyong-sik, chairman of the Central Committee of 
the Korean Social Democratic Party, on 30 December met with 
Rafiq Ahmad Sheikh, secretary general of the Pakistan People's 
Party, who is visiting our country as a member of a government 
delegation of the Islamic Republic of Pakistan and held talks in 
a friendly atmosphere. Functionaries concerned were present in 
the meeting. 
