friendship and unity between the Pakistani and Korean peoples 
will last forever and that the Pakistan People's Party actively 
supports the Korean people's struggle to reunify their 
fatherland. He touched on ways to develop the friendly 
relations between Pakistan People's Party and the Korean Social 
Democratic Party. 

